      <sentence>
        <infon key="n">5</infon>
        <offset>558</offset>
        <text>Virus-induced prokaryotic mortality increases with increasing water depth, and beneath a depth of 1,000 m nearly all of the prokaryotic heterotrophic production is transformed into organic detritus.
</text>
